{
  "id": "adv_event_2405_01_02",
  "title": "いぇー、松P",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "いや～、あの東京シーサイドとタイアップなんて\n夢みたいです～。寮でみんなに自慢しまくってやります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~‚ to think we’re collaborating with Tokyo Seaside…\nIt’s like a dream~. I’m gonna brag about it to everyone at the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.4831748962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6915196418
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "発表前はダメだからね！　でも私も楽しみです\n東京シーサイドって、私まだ行ったことなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can’t brag until it’s announced! But I’m excited too!\nI’ve never been to Tokyo Seaside before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6915196418,
      "endTime": 18.8670527457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.0753974913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、遊び気分はほどほどにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You two‚ don't get too carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0753974913,
      "endTime": 22.3309529303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5392976759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "この大きな仕事をしっかりこなして\n私達がBIG4になる足がかりにするんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to properly handle this big project\nand make it a stepping stone for us to become BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5392976759,
      "endTime": 28.706871414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9152161596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "でも今回の仕事には不安材料があるって\n{user}君は言ってたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But {user}-kun said there are some things\nthat worry him about this job‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9152161596,
      "endTime": 34.306871414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.5152161596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "僕、彼の直感を結構信じてるんだ\nこの仕事、本当に大丈夫かな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I trust his intuition quite a bit.\nI wonder if this job will really be okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5152161596,
      "endTime": 41.736009692900005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.9485494929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、トラブルが起きたら{user}さんに\n……って、今回は来られないんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if any trouble arises‚ we can ask {user}-san…\n…Oh‚ he wouldn’t be able to come this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9485494929,
      "endTime": 48.9422908145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.7476999727
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.1506355601
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、愛ちゃんが自慢の筋肉にものを言わせて\nプロデューサーをねじ伏せて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ Ai-chan can use her amazing muscles\nto overpower the producer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1506355601,
      "endTime": 55.4235833483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.5652593927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことしないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I will never do that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5652593927,
      "endTime": 57.7364158468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.9447605924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫よ、{user}さんが不在の隙間は\n私がリーダーとして埋めてみせるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry‚ as the leader‚ I’ll fill in\nfor {user}-san while he’s gone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9447605924,
      "endTime": 64.1310191944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "自己プロデュース能力を高める訓練だと思って\n頑張りましょう。って……どうしたの？　葵",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Think of this as training to improve your self-promotion skills‚\nand let's do our best. …What’s wrong‚ Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3393639401,
      "endTime": 71.3672096088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.5755543545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "……ううん、なんでもない。頑張ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ it's nothing. Let’s do our best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5755543545,
      "endTime": 75.8607471302,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6333.326721099994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8088841274,
      "endTime": 77.8088841274,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1257.7825392999955
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.8088841274
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "わっ、すっご～い！　広～い！！\nこんなにおっきなプール、初めて来たよ～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ amazing~! So spacious~!!\nI’ve never been to such a big pool~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1755482509,
      "endTime": 86.79053686399999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.9988816096
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "おおっ！　今日はタイアップCMの撮影で貸し切り\nなんでしたっけ。だから余計に広く見えますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh! Didn't they say that today was reserved for\nthe tie-up CM shoot? That's why it looks even more spacious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9988816096,
      "endTime": 94.6234393908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.8317841364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、噂のプロデューサーは\nまだ来てないみたいだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ it doesn’t look like\nthat rumored producer has arrived yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8317841364,
      "endTime": 99.58133047349999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7201.549196900004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7651174698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君の取り越し苦労なら\nいいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope {user}-kun is just\nworrying too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7651174698,
      "endTime": 103.2217615757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-producer001.m4a",
      "text": "は～い、リズノワの皆さんはじめまして！\nウェルカム、東京シーサイド！　イェー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright~‚ LizNoir‚ nice to meet you all!\nWelcome to Tokyo Seaside! Yeah~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4317841364,
      "endTime": 111.491779597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.4039442378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-producer002.m4a",
      "text": "撮影には最高の天気で、気分も上がりますね～！\nどうしたんですか～？　テンション低くないですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s perfect weather for filming‚ so let’s get pumped~!\nWhat’s wrong~? Why the low energy~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.6984462255,
      "endTime": 120.3451163763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5317831193
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "あー……こころ達のテンションが低いんじゃなくて\nそちらのテンションが高過ぎると思いまーす……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… it’s not that our energy is low‚\nit’s that your energy is too high…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5317831193,
      "endTime": 128.445071045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.6534157906
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "え、え～っと……？\nとにかくよろしくお願いしますっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ um…?\nA-anyway‚ nice to meet you!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6534157906,
      "endTime": 134.1915792618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.3999240074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "こういうノリか……\nはぁ……今までにはいなかったタイプだね",
      "translations": {
