      "text": "莉央がいいなら、「一緒にアゲアゲで胸キュンな夏を\n満喫しよーう、いえーい」とかやってもいいんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s okay with you‚ Rio‚ I’m fine with doing something like‚\n“Let’s have a superduper hyped and heart-pounding summer~ yay!”",
        "id": ""
